t = Template(
    """

        ${hi()}

        <%def name="hi()">
            hey, im hi.
            and heres ${foo()}, ${bar()}

            <%def name="foo()">
                this is foo
            </%def>

            <%def name="bar()">
                this is bar
            </%def>
        </%def>
"""
    )
eq_(flatten_result(t.render()),
    'hey, im hi. and heres this is foo , this is bar')
